SOURCE CODE:
package project1;

public class Project1 {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
                int n=4;
                int j=0,sum=0;
                for( int i=1;i<n;i++){
                    j=j+i;
                    sum=sum+j;
                    System.out.println(j);
                }
                System.out.println("The Answer is "+sum);
            
    }
    
}

OUTPUT:
1
3
6
The Answer is 10


